    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 20. Notoperla magnaspina. 12. Adult front procoxal projection, dorsal. 13. Adult foreleg, dorsal .. 14. Male genitalia, dorsal; 15. Male genitalia, lateral. 16. Female genitalia, ventral. 17. Larval front procoxal projection, dorsal. 18. Larval head, dorsal. 19. Larval tergite 10, dorsal. 20. Larval tergite 10, lateral." ;
